---
title: Creamy Corn and Bacon Chowder with a Lemony Salad and Naan Toasts
description: We couldn’t be prouda of this chowda! Our chefs have found the perfect spot between rich flavor and light, summery vibes in this soup recipe. The trick to striking that balance is gently mashing the potatoes into the milk-based broth, which creates a creamy, velvety consistency without feeling heavy. To keep things easy-breezy, there’s also a spring mix and cranberry salad on the side, plus toasty naan flatbreads.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w32-r14-1682dd1b.jpg
